==早年生平与经历==
李孟贤于1952年出生在[[华盛顿州|华盛顿州]][[西雅图|西雅图]]的{{Link-en|灯塔山社区|Beacon Hill, Seattle}} <ref name="Shih">{{cite news |last = Shih |first = Gerry |url = https://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/16/us/16bcmayor.html?_r=2&pagewanted=all |title = Mayor Lee Leads Growing Asian-American Clout |newspaper = [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date = 2011-01-15 |access-date = 2011-09-11 |url-status = live |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161109080401/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/16/us/16bcmayor.html?_r=2&pagewanted=all |archive-date = 2016-11-09 }}</ref><ref name="Dalton">{{cite news |last = Dalton |first = Andrew |url = http://sfist.com/2011/05/11/board_of_supervisors_weekly_power_r_9.php |title = Board of Supervisors Weekly Power Rankings |publisher = SFist |date = 2011-05-11 |access-date = 2011-09-11 |url-status = dead |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160517033913/http://sfist.com/2011/05/11/board_of_supervisors_weekly_power_r_9.php |archive-date = 2016-05-17 }}</ref>。他的父母在1930年代从中华民国广东省台山移民到美国。父亲曾参加[[朝鲜战争|朝鲜战争]]，当过[[厨师|厨师]]，且在西雅图市经营一家餐馆，<ref name="Shih" /><ref name="Name">{{cite news |title = Mayor Ed Lee: What's in a name? |date = 2011-08-29 |url = http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2011/08/29/MNN71KOP58.DTL&type=politics |author = Heather Knight |newspaper = San Francisco Chronicle |access-date = 2011-09-28 |url-status = live |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111108175421/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2011%2F08%2F29%2FMNN71KOP58.DTL&type=politics |archive-date = 2011-11-08 }}</ref>在李15岁时去世。<ref name="Name" />他的母亲是一名女裁缝和女服务员。<ref>{{Cite web|title=San Francisco Mayor Ed Lee, who grew up in Seattle, dies at 65|url=https://www.seattletimes.com/seattle-news/politics/san-francisco-mayor-ed-lee-who-grew-up-in-seattle-dies-at-65/|access-date=2021-10-05|date=2017-12-12|work=The Seattle Times|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211005013345/https://www.seattletimes.com/seattle-news/politics/san-francisco-mayor-ed-lee-who-grew-up-in-seattle-dies-at-65/|dead-url=no}}</ref>李一共有五个兄弟姐妹。他高中在西雅图的{{Link-en|富兰克林高中|Franklin High School (Seattle)}}就读，<ref>{{cite web |url = https://www.seattletimes.com/seattle-news/politics/san-francisco-mayor-ed-lee-who-grew-up-in-seattle-dies-at-65/ |publisher = The Seattle Times |title = San Francisco Mayor Ed Lee, who grew up in Seattle, dies at 65 |date = 2017-12-12 |author = Beekman, Daniel |access-date = 2021-10-05 |archive-date = 2021-10-05 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211005013345/https://www.seattletimes.com/seattle-news/politics/san-francisco-mayor-ed-lee-who-grew-up-in-seattle-dies-at-65/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>然后李于1974年以优异的成绩毕业于[[缅因州|缅因州]]的[[鲍登学院|鲍登学院]]。作为{{Link-en|沃森基金会|Watson Foundation}}的一位研究员，李在海外完成了长达一年的学习，然后于1978年从[[加利福尼亚大学伯克利分校法学院|加利福尼亚大学伯克利分校法学院]]毕业。<ref>{{cite web |url = http://fortune.com/2013/12/11/everyman-ed-lee/ |title = Everyman Ed Lee |first1 = Andy |last1 = Serwer |work = Fortune |date = 2013-12-11 |access-date = 2017-12-12 |url-status = live |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160530003203/http://fortune.com/2013/12/11/everyman-ed-lee/ |archive-date = 2016-05-30 }}</ref>

== 任职生涯 ==
李孟贤从1989年开始进入旧金山市政府工作，先后在多个部门任职。2005年以来，李孟贤担任旧金山行政官，负责管理多个市府部门<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 网易新闻 | title = 李孟贤成为美国旧金山首位华裔代理市长 | url = http://news.163.com/11/0112/09/6Q6JAC8C00014JB5.html | date = 2011-01-12 | accessdate = 2011-01-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110727174915/http://news.163.com/11/0112/09/6Q6JAC8C00014JB5.html | archive-date = 2011-07-27 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。2011年1月10日旧金山前市长[[加文·纽森|纽瑟姆]]提前一年结束任期，转而担任[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]副州长。旧金山市议会在翌日举行会议，11名议员一致表决同意正式任命李孟贤为代理市长，以接替[[加文·纽森|纽瑟姆]]空出的职位。这使李孟贤成为旧金山160年历史上第一位华裔、亚裔市长<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 中国新闻网 | title = 李孟贤宣誓就任旧金山160年历史上第一位华裔市长 | url = http://www.chinanews.com/hr/2011/01-12/2782349.shtml | date = 2011-01-12 | accessdate = 2011-01-12 | archive-date = 2020-11-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201106003612/http://www.chinanews.com/hr/2011/01-12/2782349.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2011年11月，李孟賢參選三藩市民選市長選舉，並得到[[舊金山華埠|華埠]]人士白蘭的支持，最後李孟賢贏得市長選舉，成為舊金山第一位民選華裔市長。

==逝世==
當地時間2017年12月11日晚，李孟賢在住所附近的[[西夫韦|Safeway超市]]購物時突發心臟病倒地，被送往{{link-en|旧金山总医院|San Francisco General Hospital}}后抢救无效，于2017年12月12日凌晨1时11分逝世，享壽65歲<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sfgate.com/news/article/San-Francisco-Mayor-Ed-Lee-dead-at-65-12423708.php |title=San Francisco Mayor Ed Lee dead at 65 |access-date=2017-12-12 |archive-date=2017-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215083239/http://www.sfgate.com/news/article/San-Francisco-Mayor-Ed-Lee-dead-at-65-12423708.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。家住當地的[[美國眾議院|眾議院]][[民主党_(美国)|民主黨]]領袖[[南希·佩洛西|佩洛西]]有向其致哀<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-42382998|title=逝者：李孟賢——美國舊金山華裔市長第一人（粵語）|accessdate=|author=|date=2017-12-17|publisher=bbc中文|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130205406/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-42382998|dead-url=no}}</ref>，中国驻旧金山前总领事[[袁南生|袁南生]]亦曾作诗《痛惋-{三藩市}-市长李孟贤不幸仙逝》悼念李孟贤<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.singtaousa.com/%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80/419983-%E7%B7%AC%E6%87%B7%E6%9C%80%E5%96%84%E8%89%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E8%80%85/|title=緬懷最善良的捍衛者|work=[[星島日報|星島日報]]|date=2017-12-18|accessdate=2019-12-17|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106003630/https://www.singtaousa.com/%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80/419983-%E7%B7%AC%E6%87%B7%E6%9C%80%E5%96%84%E8%89%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E8%80%85/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==纪念==
2019年11月13日，[[舊金山國際機場|舊金山國際機場]]国际航站楼的出发大厅被命名为“李孟贤市长国际航站楼离港大厅”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://sfbay.ca/2019/11/13/late-mayor-ed-lee-memorialized-at-sfos-departures-hall/|title=Late Mayor Ed Lee memorialized at SFO departures hall|publisher=SFBay|date=2019-11-13|accessdate=2019-12-16|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106004837/https://sfbay.ca/2019/11/13/late-mayor-ed-lee-memorialized-at-sfos-departures-hall/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

